# Tips for Using AI Built into Search Engines for Coding

## Introduction
AI-powered search engines can significantly enhance your coding workflow by providing concise answers and summarizing relevant information. This document outlines tips on how to effectively utilize these tools for coding.

## Clear and Specific Language
Use clear and specific language in your queries to ensure that AI algorithms can understand your intent and provide accurate results. Avoid jargon and vague terms that might confuse the AI models.

